{
  "stem": "7781.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was seven months pregnant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're all-- they took-- the-- after we were processed, you know, it's not like you-- after you're processed, we had to pass an-- you know, a medical test.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All those tests, we had to pass it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After that, she was pregnant seven months, so they took all the pregnant women, something, and put on the plane with the husband, and we flew to New York.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we came to New York, they took us by bus to-- to-- to the Penn Station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from there, they were sending away people to all over the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were Christian organizations, you know, all kind of-- and they used to ship them to Kansas, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Put them on the trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we-- our destination was New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we got there, I wrote to my family, whatever, you know, I never knew them, that I'm coming.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I got to Penn Station, we were sitting there, both of us, and nobody's there to-- to say hello to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we see to those people somebody's coming, and-- and-- you know, taking care of those-- this couple.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And us, nobody is there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Finally, a man came, and he looked around, he spotted us, and he walked over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He asked us whether we were Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Geslewitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I said yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he said to us, your family [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] choose not to come and take you, and take care of you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we should come, go with him, or come with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't have a choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We'd have gone with anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took us to the HIAS, you know, on Lafayette Street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
